-- Cancel changes

ExpSyntax.val: ViewMod (0) AND Level (0)='RM' AND NOT ({0,2}) OR {3,1} AND NOT ({0,2}) OR {3,3}

SQL_STMT_U.val: select CMCD_MARKCODE, cast (SUM(CMCD_SPECIALACCOUNTH + CMCD_DISPUTESGROSSH) as decimal (13,2)) as AMOUNT from :1/CMCD where CMCD_MARKCODE <> 6 and CMCD_MARKCODE <> 46 and (cast (CMCD_SPECIALACCOUNTH/:4 as decimal (15,0)) <> 0 or cast (CMCD_DISPUTESGROSSH/:4 as decimal (15,0)) <> 0) and exists ( select * from :1/CLNT where CLNT101_ADMNO = CMCD_ADMNO and CLNT102_CLNTNO = CMCD_CLNTNO and CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO = :2 and CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO = :3) group by CMCD_MARKCODE order by AMOUNT desc
